\">IG</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">14.423</biblScope> </bibl> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\"> ii 21</biblScope> </bibl> (<placeName TEIform=\"placeName\">Tauromenium</placeName>), cf. <bibl n=\"Perseus:abo:pap,BGU:822:12\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ BGU\">BGU</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">822.12</biblScope> </bibl> <date TEIform=\"date\">(iii A. D.)</date>, etc.; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">χαλκοῦ σπάνις</foreign> Men<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Mon.\">Mon.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">156</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">χαλκὸν ἔχων πῶς οὐδὲν ἔχεις μάθε</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">AP</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11.167</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> (Pollian.). </sense> <sense n=\"5\" id=\"n113163.5\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">=</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">χάλκωμα</ref></xr>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">bronze plate</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">tablet,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τὰν προξενίαν γράψαντας εἰς χαλκὸν ἀνθέμεν</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ IG\">IG</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9(1).682</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> (Corcyra, <date TEIform=\"date\">iv B. C.</date>); <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οὐετρανοὶ οἱ χωρὶς χαλκῶν,</foreign> who have not received <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">bronze copies</tr_> of the privileges granted on discharge, <bibl n=\"Perseus:abo:pap,BGU:113:5\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ BGU\">